## Learning Path

### Foundation (Beginner)
- **Lab 1**: Spark Fundamentals - Architecture, DataFrames, basic operations
- **Lab 2**: Data Loading & Transformation - Data ingestion, cleaning, validation

### Core Skills (Intermediate)
- **Lab 3**: Advanced DataFrame Operations - Joins, window functions, UDFs
- **Lab 4**: Spark SQL & Optimization - SQL operations, performance tuning
- **Lab 5**: Spark Streaming - Real-time processing, windowed operations

### Advanced (Advanced)
- **Lab 6**: MLlib Machine Learning - ML pipelines, classification, regression
- **Lab 7**: Production Deployment - Docker, Kubernetes, monitoring, CI/CD

## Total Time Estimate
- **Beginner Labs**: 2-3 hours
- **Intermediate Labs**: 4.5-6 hours
- **Advanced Labs**: 3-4 hours
- **Total**: 9.5-13 hours
